text: My Cousin Rachel is a 1952 American romantic mystery movie directed by Henry Koster and based on the 1951 novel of the same name by Daphne du Maurier. It stars Olivia de Havilland, Richard Burton, Audrey Dalton, Ronald Squire, George Dolenz and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. It was nominated for 4 Academy Awards in 1953. ==Other websites== * * Category:1952 romance movies Category:1950s historical movies Category:1950s mystery movies Category:American mystery movies Category:American romance movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Henry Koster Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies set in England Category:Movies set in the 19th century
